WEBVTT

00:10:59.387 --> 00:11:00.537
And that's me.

00:11:00.561 --> 00:11:01.712
(Laughter)

00:11:01.736 --> 00:11:04.220
Well, it's me on my sailing boat.

00:11:05.855 --> 00:11:07.386
Flirting with breeze.

00:11:08.902 --> 00:11:13.857
Well, there's not a very good reason
to show you this picture.

00:11:13.881 --> 00:11:16.815
(Laughter)

00:11:16.839 --> 00:11:18.783
I'm trying, I'm trying.

00:11:18.807 --> 00:11:23.458
You know, one thing is clear:
I love sailing, for sure.

00:11:23.482 --> 00:11:26.549
I actually also love
designing sailing boats.

00:11:27.514 --> 00:11:31.971
But I love sailing, because sailing
is associated with slowness.